    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve honestly babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still looking and driving like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in truly pristine, flawless condition\u2014not a single scratch or speck out of place! I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. It's a total dream to drive, so feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
