    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine, mint condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring a 12.5:1 compression ratio and individual throttle bodies, mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, rod bearings replaced as preventative maintenance, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by a limited-slip variable M differential and refreshed bushings. Cosmetically, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior exhibits zero bolster wear or tactile degradation. This is a rare, turn-key example for the purist collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Mint condition. Clean title. No accidents. Original paint. Garage kept. Mechanically perfect.",
