    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state; the high-grade leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear or creasing, and the interior is strictly smoke-free. Every electronic feature, from the premium audio system to the driver assistance suite, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by factory-certified technicians. It drives as tightly and smoothly as it did the day it rolled off the lot, with no leaks, noises, or vibrations. Included with the sale are all original keys, the complete set of owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a benchmark-quality vehicle that defies its age.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
